name: Payment with four carts
description: I want to pay the product

testStage.description: I want to pay the product

steps.name: Given Choose the first product and click add_to_cart1
When Choose the seecond product and click add_to_cart2
Then verify that the two product are added successfully to my cart "Sauce Labs Backpack" and "Sauce Labs Onesie"
Given i click the checkout button
When i enter the First Name "mouadh"
And i enter the Last Name  "zouaghi"
And i enter the Zip Code "1500"
And i click the continue button
And i click the finish button
Then i verify the payment with the message "Thank you for your order!"
